column4: Looks like I'll be having yet another one of your children.
Our"? Don't misunderstand. You're our slave. You exist so that we can have comfortable lives."
Still, I wonder when you're going to crack. Just having one of me should be hard enough to deal with, and yet you keep giving me more children.
One would think you want to be driven insane.
Haha, it doesn't bother me. If anything, it makes me happy.
Right. You're a pig to the core. I almost forgot about that.
